## ğŸ”§ Tech Stack

**Frontend:**
- React + Vite
- Tailwind CSS
- ShadCN UI
- Axios
- React Router

**Backend:**
- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB Atlas (Mongoose ODM)
- JWT (JSON Web Tokens)
- bcrypt
- CORS & Cookie Parser

**Deployment:**
- Vercel (Frontend)
- Render (Backend)

---

## âœ¨ Features

### ğŸ‘¥ User Features
- Sign up / Login with JWT Auth
- Browse all public job listings
- Filter jobs by **location**, **industry**, and **salary range**
- Apply to jobs (single-click application)
- View their own applications

### ğŸ¢ Company Features
- Company registration/login
- Post new jobs
- Manage (edit/delete) posted jobs
- View applicants for each job

### ğŸ›¡ï¸ Admin (Optional for future)
- Block/unblock users or companies
- Monitor job postings
- Basic analytics (planned)

